{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"31d2c71db0","title":"贺李所部应受刘邓张李指挥","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"2e62e634ec","index":0,"year":1949,"month":11,"day":27,"articleId":"31d2c71db0"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"},{"id":"dd2b275f6c","name":"毛泽东","type":"人物"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"maoquanji28","name":"毛泽东全集第28卷","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"pdf","author":"张迪杰","files":"https://raw.githubusercontent.com/banned-historical-archives/banned-historical-archives0/main/mao-quanji/28-OCR.pdf"}],"authors":[{"id":"261e5467ec","name":"毛泽东"}]},"publication_details":{"maoquanji28":{"comments":[{"id":"3556827632","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"31d2c71db0","index":1,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"这是毛泽东为中央人民政府人民革命军事委员会起草的给中共中央西南局第二书记、中国人民解放军第二野战军司令员刘佰承，中共中央西南局第一书记、中国人民解放军第二野战军政治委员兼西南军区政治委员邓小平，中共中央西南局第三书记、中国人民解放军西南军区司令员贺龙和川西北军政委员会副主任李井泉的电报。"},{"id":"492d526559","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"31d2c71db0","index":2,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"康，指西康，旧省名，1955年撤销。"},{"id":"a7521fb305","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"31d2c71db0","index":3,"part_index":-99,"offset":-99,"text":"刘，指刘伯承。邓，指邓小平。张，指张际春，当时任中国人民解放军第二野战军副政治委员兼政治部主任。李，指李达，当时任中国人民解放军第二野战军参课长。"}],"contents":[{"id":"38896f4a19","type":"title","text":"贺李所部应受刘邓张李指挥”","index":0,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"31d2c71db0"},{"id":"3556827632","type":"paragraph","text":"刘、邓，贺、李：","index":1,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"31d2c71db0"},{"id":"492d526559","type":"paragraph","text":"（一）为协同一致上（全）歼川、康各敌之目的，军委决定贺、季所部（十八兵团及其他）应受刘、邓、张、季指挥，我们不直接指挥贺、李，以免分政。（二）贺、李发给刘、邓之电报，同时发一份给我们。（三）以上望遵照为要","index":2,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"31d2c71db0"},{"id":"a7521fb305","type":"paragraph","text":"中央军委","index":3,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"31d2c71db0"},{"id":"5497e3883c","type":"paragraph","text":"十一月二十七日","index":4,"publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"31d2c71db0"}],"page":{"id":"0cd51fc096","publicationId":"maoquanji28","articleId":"31d2c71db0","start":45,"end":45}}}},"__N_SSG":true}